 Do not let it burn while frying. If you add the cashew nuts, it will get burnt fast. Once it becomes hot, we shall keep it aside in this pan. Once it cools down, we shall grind it in the mixi. Do not keep it in the same pan after frying. Since it is hot, it may get burnt.

10
00:03:38,730 --> 00:04:07,401
 Next we are going to fry some onions for this biriyani. For that I have cut 2 onions into thin slices. If you have a slicer, you can grate it and make it thin. Only then you can fry it well. If you want to avoid this stage, you can do it. You can even add 2 onions to the masala. But for this you can make a tastier biriyani. Heat 2-3 batches of oil and fry it.

