 When the oil is hot add 1 1⁄4 cup crushed ginger,1⁄4 cup crushed garlic and 5-6 green chillies. You can adjust the spice according to your taste. If the chillies are very spicy, 5 will be enough. We dont need more spice for biriyani. Now add this to the oil.

