 Now add 1tbsp of lemon juice to this. We have added 1.5tbsp of curd. Now check the salt needed for the chicken. If you want you can add more salt to the masala and cook it. You dont have to add water to this. The chicken will take 10-12mts to get cooked. Cook this on medium to low flame.

22
00:08:30,415 --> 00:08:57,684
 The chicken has been cooked well. We haven't added any water to it. We need to dry it well. Before that we shall add 3tbsp grated coconut and 8-10 cashew nuts to the mixi and grind it. If you soak it in water for a while, it will be easy to grind it. Do not add more coconut while grinding. If you add more, the masala will be more.

23
00:08:58,697 --> 00:09:15,217
 Mix all these well. You can use this tip for any biriyani. You can add cashew nuts or coconut as per your taste. Never add more when adding coconut.

24
00:09:15,217 --> 00:09:34,287
 Add all these and cook the chicken well. The masala should thicken more. The chicken should be cooked well. If the chicken is not cooked well, the biriyani wont taste good. The chicken should be cooked well. So let's wait till then.

25
00:09:35,047 --> 00:10:00,595
 Now the gravy is ready. We need this much of gravy for this biriyani. Lets garnish this biriyani with some coriander leaves and mint leaves. Not much. Just for the flavour. Add 2 pinches of biriyani masala at this time. Close this well and keep aside. Now lets make the ghee rice for the biriyani. Dont forget to close it well. It will lose its smell.

26
00:10:00,831 --> 00:10:25,434
 Now lets begin to make the rice. We are going to make this biriyani with 3.5 cups of Jeerakashala rice. This biriyani is always good with Jeerakashala rice. You can make it with Basmati rice too. But it will be tastier. Many have asked me which brand I am using when making Jeerakashala rice. I am using Nirapara Wayanadan Kaima Jeerakashala.

27
00:10:25,434 --> 00:10:55,422
 This is the rice that I have chosen.Its a good smell and I think its a good rice The rice of Golden Chef is also good.You can use any rice you want When we take this type of rice,we need to soak it for some time before making the ghee rice If you dont soak it for some time,the rice will be hard to chew We can use the rice that we get in Kerala directly in ghee rice

28
00:10:55,422 --> 00:11:23,231
 I have used the golden chef of Neerabara and our Natchez Joshi. We have to soak this for 20-25mts. We need 3.5 cups of rice. Wash it well and then soak it for 20-25mts or maximum 30mts. Then we shall make soft ghee rice. When we soak it and wash it, add little salt and wash it well. Then we will get a good rice.

29
00:11:23,721 --> 00:11:42,892
 Heat a pan for making ghee rice. Add 2-3tbsp ghee to it. You can add ghee as per your taste. If you add more ghee, the ghee rice will get a tasty glising. We are not making biriyani daily. So add ghee as per your taste.

30
00:11:43,380 --> 00:12:08,879
 When the ghee is hot add 6 cloves,4-5 cardamoms,2 pieces of cinnamon,2 pinches of fennel seeds. If you want you can add more fennel seeds. Now add 1tbsp of finely chopped onions. You can adjust the amount of onions according to your taste.

