42
00:16:17,278 --> 00:16:41,495
 Add little bit of the rest of the biriyani masala to this. Now add little lemon juice over this. This helps to get rid of the sourness of the rice. Make sure to add lemon juice according to the sourness of the masala.

43
00:16:41,831 --> 00:17:10,132
