 So that the smell of the biriyani doesn't go out. You can cover it well. Its difficult to stick it with maida flour. Some people find it difficult to stick it in a non stick pan. If it is like that, you can cover it with a foil paper. Its easy to use when you are in Kerala. It will be easy to stick it on the outside of the stove. Lets cover it with some maida.

